&lt;li&gt;Process, sort, and manage physical and digital mail; flag action items and ensure timely responses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and organize files, correspondence, and records on behalf of both executives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the point of contact for office logistics, including supply management and any SLC-based operational needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare expense reports, track reimbursements, and liaise with our finance function as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to streamline workflows and proactively implement quality-of-life improvements for leadership&lt;/li&gt;
