&lt;li&gt;Proven experience as an executive assistant, personal assistant, a similar administrative support role, or any service-oriented position&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional organizational skills and the ability to manage multiple priorities simultaneously without dropping the ball&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal communication skills; able to represent leadership professionally in correspondence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High degree of discretion and judgment when handling confidential or sensitive information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive problem-solver who anticipates needs and takes initiative without being asked&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable operating in a fast-moving startup environment where priorities can shift quickly&lt;/li&gt;
